name: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF James Albert FROST.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties: In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF James Albert FROST.

opinions.text: James Albert Frost, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.

casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF James Albert FROST.
No. D-2785.
Supreme Court of the United States
Aug. 11, 2014.
Opinion
